<div style="margin-bottom: 10px">
  <h3>
    <a href="/p/whonix/blog/2012/12/whonix-045-tor-browser-updater-broken-and-workaround/">Whonix 0.4.5 Tor Browser updater broken and workaround</a>
  </h3>
  <div class="markdown_content"><p>At the moment updating Tor Browser inside Whonix does no longer work.</p>
<p>Bug report, discussion and help thread:<br />
<a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/discussion/general/thread/6122990d/">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/discussion/general/thread/6122990d/</a></p>
<p>I am working on a fix.</p>
<p>In meanwhile use please:<br />
<a href="http://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/ManualTBupdate/">http://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/ManualTBupdate/</a></p></div>
  <em class="grid-19">
    Posted by <a href="/u/adrelanos/">
    
  
    <img src="https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e6d471603b9691707b0445c54f04d460?r=pg"
