  <h3>
    <a href="/p/whonix/blog/2012/11/guest-additions-for-virtual-box-warnings-and-article-updated/">Guest Additions for Virtual Box warnings and article updated</a>
  </h3>
  <div class="markdown_content"><p>If you are using Virtual Box guest additions (even though it's recommend against), you are advised to read the Guest Additions chapter.</p>
<p><a href="https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/OptionalConfigurations/#virtualbox-guest-additions">https://sourceforge.net/p/whonix/wiki/OptionalConfigurations/#virtualbox-guest-additions</a></p></div>
  <em class="grid-19">
    Posted by <a href="/u/adrelanos/">
    
  
